items.title: Trump Wins Appeal Over Freeze on Foreign Aid
items.description: A federal appeals court on Wednesday lifted a lower court injunction that required the Trump administration to continue making foreign aid payments.

items.title: Fmr N.Y. Gov. Paterson to Endorse Adams in Mayoral Race
items.description: Former New York Gov. David Paterson announced on Wednesday that he will later in the afternoon publicly endorse Mayor Eric Adams for reelection.

items.title: Israeli FM Sa'ar Tells Newsmax Mission 'No' to Two-State Solution
items.description: Israel "will not allow" its land to be used for the creation of a Palestinian state, Foreign Minister Gideon Sa'ar said Wednesday.
